item.title: Shoes
item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

Depending on where you are situated and who you hang around with will define what looks good to you and your friends etc.

To me, skating clothing aren’t cool whatsoever. Some of my friends are skaters and their like omg this that skater brand and I’m like okay sweet when I’m really thinking no skater brand is going to appeal to mainstream normal people. You want something stylish, its not going to be skater stuff as I said before its who you want to please. I can lie to you and say I dress the way I do because I like it but thats not the 100% reason, the other reason is too look decent to people I’m attracted to etc.
